      <title>富达计划在市政债券市场推出最新一轮共同基金转 ETF 计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/fidelity-plans-latest-mutual-fund-to-etf-flips-in-muni-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富达投资 (Fidelity Investments) 正考虑将其两只市政债券共同基金转换为交易所交易基金，此举凸显了美国 10 万亿美元市场的受欢迎程度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/fidelity-plans-latest-mutual-fund-to-etf-flips-in-muni-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国能源部承诺提供 11 亿美元贷款后，EVgo 股价上涨 64%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/evgo-jumps-37-after-1-1-billion-loan-commitment-from-doe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电动汽车充电公司 EVgo Inc. 获得美国能源部高达 10.5 亿美元的有条件贷款担保以扩建其充电网络后，其股价创下三年多来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/evgo-jumps-37-after-1-1-billion-loan-commitment-from-doe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:28:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突和美国数据拖累新兴货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pause-in-china-rally-sparks-wider-drop-in-emerging-market-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币周四走弱，因对中东冲突的担忧推动了对避险美元的需求，而美国数据支持了人们对美联储将放缓降息步伐的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pause-in-china-rally-sparks-wider-drop-in-emerging-market-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
